# Vue 3 Project Structure Template

## Standard Project Structure

```
my-vue-app/
├── public/                 # Static assets
│   ├── favicon.ico
│   └── index.html
├── src/
│   ├── assets/            # Imported assets (images, styles)
│   │   ├── logo.png
│   │   └── main.css
│   ├── components/        # Reusable components
│   │   ├── common/        # Common UI components
